<br>
Iceflame would only help those who have cold nukes.  That would be Wizards and Shaman primarily, Beastlord to a lesser degree, and druid sometimes.  Not exactly engineered to get us into every group, though helping the Shaman can't hurt.<br>
<br>
Now, a Manaflare spell that focused Magic based nukes would catch just about everyone except Shaman and Beastlords... <p><br>
